column5: Looking to go fishing tomorrow hate fishing alone, anyone got time to do some bass fishing?  Where we going? Simcoe? (I don't know the lake well)  I am in Orangeville and would like to keep travel time around 1 hour.  I got the boat!  See ya tomorrow!!!
Nice offer!! If early week was a time off,maybe?.
Anyone?  What if I drive further?  1.5 hours?  That puts me at scugog, or sparrow.  Any body fish Lake Eugenia?
Well, think I give up for the night.  I know it was short notice, thanks to those who replied.  If you see this and want to go, PM me
Awesome!!! see ya at 530 John  Sorry seat filled. Thanks guys
